<item>
            <title>[MAHOUT-609] Add an option to make RecommenderJob write out it&apos;s computed item similarities</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MAHOUT-609</link>
                <project id="12310751" key="MAHOUT">Mahout</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;As RecommenderJob already includes the computation of similar items, we should an add option that makes it write out those similar items in the same format as ItemSimilarityJob does, so that users interested in both recommendations and similar items do not have to run two jobs.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12498008">MAHOUT-609</key>
            <summary>Add an option to make RecommenderJob write out it&apos;s computed item similarities</summary>
